{"tid":2129950,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[黃碧雲2.0] 譚香文又參選立法會會計界白撞","createTime":"2020-07-29T03:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T06:27:32.000Z","uid":7814,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"14cb9f214ad99f943be0718add8b038e0787d8f8","tid":2129950,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:08:04.000Z","msg":"同區選一撚樣, 一開波講到幾偉大去填白區, 跟住人地做琴一半就走去撞走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190907/s00001/1567868523825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190907%2Fs00001%2F1567868523825&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=9882246a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190907%2Fs00001%2F1567868523825&h=fa4d084d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190907/s00001/1567868523825</a><br />\n<br />\n而家立法會又係咁, 一開波又話填區又剩, 結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074772&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=770e58dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074772&h=1f702917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074772</a><br />\n<blockquote>前會計界立法會議員、黃大仙區議員譚香文正考慮出戰工業界（第二），她早前已獲公司授權成為選民，「我哋要為佢哋（年輕人）打最後一場仗」，望讓「仔仔囡囡」在艱難的時勢感到一絲希望。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>她期望有更多年輕人參選功能組別，包括挑戰已連任數屆的民主派，「要換血喇，佢哋嘅聲音先係最重要，你諗吓，我哋最多淨返20年就『上天家』，但佢哋仲有起碼60年喎。」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/2595/32870953146_63ba7b8895_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F2595%2F32870953146_63ba7b8895_b.jpg&h=10421217&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7a52c160d7b254947b50ad3eb701218fb076c3d","tid":2129950,"uid":7814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:09:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/E4FIJ5H4GBKVBHIBOW7QJ6KDY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FE4FIJ5H4GBKVBHIBOW7QJ6KDY4%2F&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=6656080d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FE4FIJ5H4GBKVBHIBOW7QJ6KDY4%2F&h=c04210ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/E4FIJ5H4GBKVBHIBOW7QJ6KDY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n會計界則有兩人今日報名，包括黃大仙區議員、曾任會計界立法會議員的譚香文及未有申報政治聯繫的林全智，連同爭取連任的梁繼昌及再戰的林智遠，四人爭一席。"},{"pid":"1a6497d62ee87ed328d6bb3538f8667a4fe95d5d","tid":2129950,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6b7029ac129e851a425b5e747e738f99da38c7","tid":2129950,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515457e4e8b617ae374b96d7e9383c88b3b9670a","tid":2129950,"uid":303495,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:13:50.000Z","msg":"譚香文考慮出戰<span class=\"red\">回歸後皆由建制派自動當選的工業界（第二）</span><br />\n樓主一係盲一係0.5"},{"pid":"4962bfae65b4c4172b531f23d1d276eeefcec6e4","tid":2129950,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T03:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b4f89f4608f61422079670da62e693e2a7321a","tid":2129950,"uid":9564,"like":1,